                        Add a script to your <code>package.json</code> to automate the build process:
                    </p>
                    <pre class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg mt-2 overflow-auto text-sm md:text-base">
<code class="language-json">
"scripts": {
  "build:css": "tailwindcss -i ./wwwroot/css/site.css -o ./wwwroot/css/output.css",
  "watch:css": "tailwindcss -i ./wwwroot/css/site.css -o ./wwwroot/css/output.css --watch"
}
</code>
                    </pre>
